[This outbreak follows a familiar pattern in Europe of revelation of
inadequacies in vaccine coverage through the introduction of virus by
migrants from less well-protected regions.

A map and description of Murcia can be accessed at:
<http://www.alicante-spain.com/murcia.html>. The
HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Spain is available at:
<http://healthmap.org/r/01eT>. - Mod.CP]
